query:
insert into
                product (id, as_of, app_data)
            values
                ($1, $2, jsonb($3))
            returning
                id as "id!: ProductId",
                json(app_data) as "app_data!: sqlx::types::Json<ProductData>",
                null as "parent?: sqlx::types::Json<(ProductId, f64)>",
                json_object(id, 1.0) as "basis!: sqlx::types::Json<Basis<ProductId>>"
